code: // ------------------------------------------------------------------------ // Accumulator // ------------------------------------------------------------------------ /**  * Consider using {@link #add(int)} instead for primitive integer values  */ @Override public void add(Integer value) {     this.max = Math.max(this.max, value). }
@Override public void merge(Accumulator<Integer, Integer> other) {     this.max = Math.max(this.max, other.getLocalValue()). }
@Override public IntMaximum clone() {     IntMaximum clone = new IntMaximum().     clone.max = this.max.     return clone. }
